<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM6.1.8">
<l>kātalcey tiḷaiyavar kalavitarum</l>
<l>vētaṉai viṉaiyatu veruvutalām</l>
<l>ātali ṉuṉataṭi yaṇukuvaṉṉāṉ</l>
<l>pōtalar neṭumuṭip puṇṇiyaṉē</l>
<l rend="indent">āṇṭāyuṉaik kāṇpatō raruḷeṉak karuḷutiyēl,</l>
<l rend="indent">vēṇṭēṉmaṉai vāḻkkaiyai viṇṇakar mēyavaṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Yes, there is dread of the painful karma</l>
<l>Which union with young women causes, having made love;</l>
<l>Therefore I approach your feet,</l>
<l>Pure lord with a tall crown where buds blossom,</l>
<l rend="indent">Master, if you bless me with the one blessing of seeing you,</l>
<l rend="indent">I would not want this domestic life, you who dwells in Viṇṇakar.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
